msgid "2 &ndash; if kmmAccounts.isStockAccount = \"Y&rdquor;"
msgstr "2 &ndash; if kmmAccounts.isStockAccount = \"Y&rdquor;"

#. Tag: title
#: details-database.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid "Field formats"
msgstr "Formati polj"

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several of the data fields are held in an internal format which may not be "
"immediately useful to external programs. In these cases, the information has "
"been duplicated in both internal and external formats."
msgstr ""
"Več podatkovnih polj je shranjenih v notranji obliki, ki morda ne bo takoj "
"uporabna za zunanje programe. V teh primerih so bile informacije podvojene v "
"notranji in zunanji obliki."

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Monetary amounts and share values are shown both in numerator/denominator "
"format, and, with a field name suffixed with <quote> <literal>Formatted</"
"literal> </quote>, in the form as typically displayed."
msgstr ""
"Denarni zneski in vrednosti delnic so prikazani v obliki števca/imenovalca "
"in z imenom polja s pripono <quote> <literal>Oblikovano</literal> </quote> v "
"obliki, kot je običajno prikazana."

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similarly, some fields, such as account type appear both as a numeric code, "
"and in a field suffixed '<literal>String</literal>' in the form and language "
"of the application."
msgstr ""
"Podobno se nekatera polja, kot je vrsta računa, prikažejo kot številska koda "
"in v polju s pripono '<literal>Niz</literal>' v obliki in jeziku aplikacije."

#. Tag: title
#: details-database.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updating your data"
msgstr "Posodabljanje vaših podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Having data in an industry standard format does give you the ability to "
"modify it outside the &kmymoney; application. DO NOT DO IT unless you really "
"know what you are doing, and always be certain to make a backup copy of your "
"data first. If you get it wrong, &kmymoney; may not be able to access your "
"data, and you could even end up losing it altogether. You have been warned!"
msgstr ""
"Če imate podatke v standardnem formatu za panogo, jih lahko spreminjate "
"zunaj aplikacije &kmymoney;. NE STORITE TEGA, razen če res veste, kaj "
"počnete, in vedno najprej naredite varnostno kopijo svojih podatkov. Če se "
"zmotite, &kmymoney; morda ne boste mogli dostopati do svojih podatkov in jih "
"lahko celo popolnoma izgubite. Bili ste opozorjeni!"

#. Tag: title
#: details-database.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stored queries"
msgstr "Shranjene poizvedbe"

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most database systems allow you to store commonly used queries and "
"procedures, and in some cases, these may be held as tables or other objects "
"within your database itself. As you will have guessed from the above, all "
"the tables used by &kmymoney; begin with the lowercase letters "
"'<literal>kmm</literal>'. This standard will be maintained, and only tables "
"beginning with these letters will be updated. Thus, provided you avoid these "
"in the naming of your queries &etc;, you should not experience any problems."
msgstr ""
"Večina sistemov podatkovnih baz vam omogoča shranjevanje pogosto "
"uporabljenih poizvedb in postopkov, v nekaterih primerih pa so ti lahko "
"shranjeni kot tabele ali drugi objekti v sami bazi podatkov. Kot ste uganili "
"iz zgornjega, so vse tabele, ki jih uporablja &kmymoney; začnejo se z malimi "
"črkami '<literal>kmm</literal>'. Ta standard bo ohranjen in posodobljene "
"bodo samo tabele, ki se začnejo s temi črkami. Pod pogojem, da se temu "
"izognete pri poimenovanju vaših poizvedb &etc;, ne bi smeli imeti težav."

#. Tag: title
#: details-database.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manual database creation"
msgstr "Ročna izdelava baze podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section covers more advanced database usage and may be skipped by the "
"general user."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek pokriva naprednejšo uporabo baze podatkov in ga lahko splošni "
"uporabnik preskoči."

#. Tag: title
#: details-database.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "When to use"
msgstr "Kdaj uporabiti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There may be occasions when &kmymoney; is unable to create the database "
"automatically, or creates it without some options required by the user. For "
"example, the database system used may not completely conform to standard SQL "
"usage, or support may be introduced for new systems which have not been "
"fully tested in &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Včasih lahko &kmymoney; baze podatkov ne more ustvariti samodejno ali pa jo "
"ustvari brez nekaterih možnosti, ki jih zahteva uporabnik. Na primer, "
"uporabljeni sistem baze podatkov morda ni popolnoma v skladu s standardno "
"uporabo SQL ali pa je uvedena podpora za nove sisteme, ki niso bili v celoti "
"preizkušeni v &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Prior to using this facility, you should try just creating the database "
"entry itself (&ie; with the <literal>CREATE DATABASE</literal> statement). "
"Provided the database exists, &kmymoney; may well be able to create the "
"tables, &etc; in the normal database save procedure described above."
msgstr ""
"Preden uporabite to možnost, poskusite samo ustvariti vnos v bazo podatkov "
"(&ie; s stavkom <literal>CREATE DATABASE</literal>). Če baza podatkov "
"obstaja, &kmymoney; morda lahko ustvarite tabele &etc; v običajnem postopku "
"shranjevanja baze podatkov, opisanem zgoraj."

#. Tag: title
#: details-database.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generating the SQL"
msgstr "Generiranje SQL"

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this fails, it is possible to generate the basic SQL commands needed to "
"create the various tables, views, and indexes required by the application. "
"Select the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Generate "
"Database SQL</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item. This will present the "
"following dialog:"
msgstr ""
"Če to ne uspe, je mogoče ustvariti osnovne ukaze SQL, potrebne za "
"ustvarjanje različnih tabel, pogledov in indeksov, ki jih zahteva "
"aplikacija. Izberite menijsko postavko <menuchoice> <guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Generate Database SQL</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. To "
"bo prikazalo naslednje pogovorno okno:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-database.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>generate sql to create a database</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>generiraj sql za ustvarjanje baze podatkov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-database.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>generate sql to create a database</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>generiraj sql za ustvarjanje baze podatkov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On selecting the database type, the appropriate SQL will appear in the "
"<guilabel>SQL for creation</guilabel> text box; this can be edited by the "
"user, or saved to a text file by clicking <guibutton>Save SQL</guibutton>. "
"In the latter case, the database must be created using the administrative "
"functions provided by the database system."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete vrsto baze podatkov, se bo ustrezen SQL prikazal v besedilnem "
"polju <guilabel>SQL za ustvarjanje</guilabel>; to lahko ureja uporabnik ali "
"pa ga shrani v besedilno datoteko s klikom na <guibutton>Shrani SQL</"
"guibutton>. V slednjem primeru mora biti baza podatkov ustvarjena z uporabo "
"upravnih funkcij, ki jih zagotavlja sistem baze podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If after editing the text in the dialog, you want &kmymoney; to create the "
"database, you will need to complete the other fields in the dialog, as "
"detailed in <link linkend=\"details.database.selectdatabase\">Creating a "
"Database</link> above, and click <guibutton>Create Tables</guibutton>. Note "
"that, except in the case of SQLite, you will need either to include a "
"suitable <literal>CREATE DATABASE</literal> statement as the first command, "
"or have previously issued such a command externally to &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Če po urejanju besedila v pogovornem oknu želite &kmymoney; če želite "
"ustvariti bazo podatkov, boste morali izpolniti druga polja v pogovornem "
"oknu, kot je podrobno opisano v <link linkend=\"details.database."
"selectdatabase\">Ustvarjanje baze podatkov</link> zgoraj, in kliknite "
"<guibutton>Ustvari tabele</guibutton>. Upoštevajte, da boste morali, razen v "
"primeru SQLite, kot prvi ukaz vključiti ustrezen stavek <literal>CREATE "
"DATABASE</literal> ali pa tak ukaz predhodno izdati zunaj &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: title
#: details-database.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid "Warning"
msgstr "Opozorilo"

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should be very careful editing the definitions of any of the basic "
"tables or views (those with names beginning with '<literal>kmm</literal>'.) "
"Some changes, such as increasing the length of an integer field, may have "
"little impact, but you should not remove or change the sequence of any "
"fields, or &kmymoney; may refuse to function, or may corrupt your data."
msgstr ""
"Pri urejanju definicij katere koli osnovne tabele ali pogleda (tistih z "
"imeni, ki se začnejo z '<literal>kmm</literal>') morate biti zelo previdni. "
"Nekatere spremembe, kot je povečanje dolžine polja celega števila, lahko "
"imajo majhen vpliv, vendar ne smete odstraniti ali spremeniti zaporedja polj "
"ali &kmymoney; saj lahko zavrne delovanje ali poškoduje vaše podatke."

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While adding or removing indexes may improve performance, you should also be "
"aware that the opposite may happen. Some knowledge of the internal operation "
"of &kmymoney; may help to get the best performance in these circumstances."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav lahko dodajanje ali odstranjevanje indeksov izboljša zmogljivost, se "
"morate zavedati, da se lahko zgodi nasprotno. Nekaj ​​znanja o notranjem "
"delovanju &kmymoney; lahko pomaga doseči najboljše rezultate v teh "
"okoliščinah."

#. Tag: title
#: details-database.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encryption"
msgstr "Šifriranje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encryption of data in your database is not currently supported."
msgstr "Šifriranje podatkov v vaši bazi trenutno ni podprto."

